[LAUGHTER]

01:00:40.006 --> 01:00:41.850
It's like a few.

01:00:41.850 --> 01:00:45.150
How many of you feel
like kind of bad?

01:00:45.150 --> 01:00:47.100
Like we're at a pathogen
conference, so yeah,

01:00:47.100 --> 01:00:48.390
many of you feel bad.

01:00:48.390 --> 01:00:50.460
And how many of you feel
like it's complicated?

01:00:50.460 --> 01:00:52.180
[LAUGHTER]

01:00:52.180 --> 01:00:52.792
Yeah.

01:00:52.792 --> 01:00:54.250
Like, I feel like
it's complicated.

01:00:54.250 --> 01:00:56.700
You know on one hand, it's
like the most commonly used

01:00:56.700 --> 01:00:58.590
bacterial model organism.

01:00:58.590 --> 01:01:00.270
Every biology lab
in this country

01:01:00.270 --> 01:01:02.790
and probably in the
